## Workflow 1 — تعديل الـ Messenger Workflow الحالي

### أين تُضاف الـ Nodes الجديدة؟
**بعد** `Smart Router Input1` مباشرةً، **قبل** `AI Agent4`.

```
[Smart Router Input1]
       ↓
[★ NODE 1: Get Timer Config]   ← MySQL
       ↓
[★ NODE 2: Get Lead]           ← MySQL
       ↓
[★ NODE 3: Get Open Tickets]   ← MySQL
       ↓
[AI Agent4]  (موجود - بدون تغيير)
       ↓
[Switch6]    (موجود - بدون تغيير)
       ↓
 ┌─[GENERAL_INFO]──────────────────── بدون تغيير ──────────────────────┐
 ├─[DEEP_INFO_PERSONAL / CORPORATION]                                   │
 │      ↓                                                               │
 │  [★ NODE 4: Ticket Manager]  ← Code Node                            │
 │      ↓                                                               │
 │  [★ NODE 5: Execute Ticket SQL] ← MySQL                             │
 │      ↓                                                               │
 │  [★ NODE 6: Save Timer] ← MySQL                                     │
 │      ↓                                                               │
 │  [Deep Course Info1] (موجود - بدون تغيير)                           │
 ├─[TECHNICAL_SUPPORT]                                                  │
 │      ↓                                                               │
 │  [★ NODE 4: Ticket Manager] ← Code Node                             │
 │      ↓ (نفس 5 و 6)                                                  │
 │  [Code in JavaScript28] (موجود)                                     │
 ├─[COMPLAINT]                                                          │
 │      ↓                                                               │
 │  [★ NODE 4: Ticket Manager] ← Code Node                             │
 │      ↓ (نفس 5 و 6)                                                  │
 │  [رد عام]                                                            │
 └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
       ↓
[HTTP Request16] (موجود - بدون تغيير)
```

---

### ★ NODE 1: Get Timer Config — MySQL Node

**النوع:** `MySQL → Execute Query`

```sql
SELECT title, value FROM atc_config WHERE title LIKE 'crm_%timer%'
```

بعده أضف **Code Node** لتحويل النتائج إلى متغيرات:

```javascript
// Code Node: "Parse Timer Config"
const items = $input.all();
const config = {};
items.forEach(item => {
  config[item.json.title] = parseInt(item.json.value);
});

// نمرر config مع بيانات الرسالة الأصلية
const input = $items("Smart Router Input1")[0].json;
return [{ json: { ...input, timerConfig: config } }];
```

---

### ★ NODE 2: Get Lead — MySQL Node

**النوع:** `MySQL → Execute Query`

```sql
SELECT 
  l.id as lead_id,
  l.user_id_fk,
  l.last_interaction_time,
  lsp.platform_user_id,
  lsp.display_name,
  lsp.gender
FROM crm_leads l
JOIN crm_lead_social_profiles lsp ON l.id = lsp.crm_lead_id
WHERE lsp.platform = 'facebook'
  AND lsp.platform_user_id = '{{ $("Smart Router Input1").first().json.sessionId }}'
LIMIT 1
```

بعده أضف **Code Node** للتعامل مع حالة عدم وجود Lead:

```javascript
// Code Node: "Handle Lead"
const input = $items("Parse Timer Config")[0].json;
const leads = $input.all();

let lead_id = null;
let user_id_fk = null;
let last_interaction_time = null;

if (leads.length > 0 && leads[0].json.lead_id) {
  lead_id = leads[0].json.lead_id;
  user_id_fk = leads[0].json.user_id_fk;
  last_interaction_time = leads[0].json.last_interaction_time;
} else {
  // Lead جديد — سنُنشئه في Ticket Manager
}

return [{ json: {
  ...input,
  lead_id,
  user_id_fk,
  last_interaction_time
}}];
```

---

### ★ NODE 3: Get Open Tickets — MySQL Node

**النوع:** `MySQL → Execute Query`

```sql
SELECT 
  t.id as ticket_id,
  t.crm_ticket_type_id,
  t.sales_level_id,
  t.running_program_id,
  t.running_program_type,
  t.last_timer_time,
  tt.code as ticket_type_code,
  sl.code as sales_level_code
FROM crm_tickets t
JOIN crm_ticket_types tt ON t.crm_ticket_type_id = tt.id
LEFT JOIN crm_sales_ticket_levels sl ON t.sales_level_id = sl.id
WHERE t.crm_lead_id = {{ $json.lead_id || 0 }}
  AND t.closed = 0
ORDER BY t.created DESC
```

بعده **Code Node** لتجميع كل بيانات السياق:

```javascript
// Code Node: "Build Context"
const input = $items("Handle Lead")[0].json;
const tickets = $input.all().map(t => t.json);

return [{ json: {
  ...input,
  openTickets: tickets
}}];
```

---

### ★ NODE 4: Ticket Manager — Code Node الرئيسي

هذا هو "عقل" النظام. يُوضع بعد **كل فرع** يحتاج تذكرة (DEEP_INFO, TECHNICAL, COMPLAINT).

```javascript
// Code Node: "Ticket Manager"
// يعمل بعد Switch6 في فروع: DEEP_INFO_*, TECHNICAL_SUPPORT, COMPLAINT

const ctx = $items("Build Context")[0].json;
const routerValue = ctx.output ? ctx.output.trim() : '';
const openTickets  = ctx.openTickets || [];
const timerConfig  = ctx.timerConfig || {};

// إيجاد التذاكر المصنّفة
const salesTicket     = openTickets.find(t => t.crm_ticket_type_id >= 1 && t.crm_ticket_type_id <= 24);
const complaintTicket = openTickets.find(t => t.ticket_type_code === 'COMPLAINT');
const techTicket      = openTickets.find(t => t.ticket_type_code === 'TECHNICAL_SUPPORT');

let action = null; // 'create' | 'update' | 'skip'
let ticketData = {};
let timerData  = {};
const now = new Date();

// ──────────────────────────────────────────────
// DEEP_INFO_PERSONAL أو DEEP_INFO_CORPORATION
// ──────────────────────────────────────────────
if (routerValue.startsWith('DEEP_INFO')) {
  if (salesTicket) {
    // CASE B — تذكرة مبيعات مفتوحة → حدّث وأعد Timer
    action = 'update';
    ticketData = { ticket_id: salesTicket.ticket_id };
    timerData  = {
      ticket_id: salesTicket.ticket_id,
      timer_type: 'PRE_SALE_FOLLOWUP',
      minutes: timerConfig.crm_pre_sale_timer_minutes || 1435
    };
  } else {
    // CASE A — لا تذاكر → أنشئ تذكرة جديدة
    action = 'create';
    ticketData = {
      ticket_type_id: 1, // DEEP_INFO_PERSONAL type
      title: `استفسار مبيعات — ${new Date().toISOString().slice(0,10)}`
    };
    timerData = {
      timer_type: 'PRE_SALE_FOLLOWUP',
      minutes: timerConfig.crm_pre_sale_timer_minutes || 1435
    };
  }
}

// ──────────────────────────────────────────────
// TECHNICAL_SUPPORT
// ──────────────────────────────────────────────
else if (routerValue === 'TECHNICAL_SUPPORT') {
  if (techTicket) {
    // CASE C — نفس التذكرة
    action = 'update';
    ticketData = { ticket_id: techTicket.ticket_id };
    timerData  = {
      ticket_id: techTicket.ticket_id,
      timer_type: 'TECHNICAL_SUPPORT_FOLLOWUP',
      minutes: timerConfig.crm_followup_timer_minutes || 1435
    };
  } else {
    action = 'create';
    ticketData = {
      ticket_type_id: 25, // TECHNICAL_SUPPORT type_id
      title: `دعم فني — ${new Date().toISOString().slice(0,10)}`
    };
    timerData = {
      timer_type: 'TECHNICAL_SUPPORT_FOLLOWUP',
      minutes: timerConfig.crm_technical_timer_minutes || 240
    };
  }
}

// ──────────────────────────────────────────────
// COMPLAINT
// ──────────────────────────────────────────────
else if (routerValue === 'COMPLAINT') {
  if (complaintTicket) {
    action = 'update';
    ticketData = { ticket_id: complaintTicket.ticket_id };
    timerData  = {
      ticket_id: complaintTicket.ticket_id,
      timer_type: 'COMPLAINT_FOLLOWUP',
      minutes: timerConfig.crm_followup_timer_minutes || 1435
    };
  } else {
    action = 'create';
    ticketData = {
      ticket_type_id: 26, // COMPLAINT type_id
      title: `شكوى — ${new Date().toISOString().slice(0,10)}`
    };
    timerData = {
      timer_type: 'COMPLAINT_FOLLOWUP',
      minutes: timerConfig.crm_complaint_timer_minutes || 240
    };
  }
}

return [{ json: {
  ...ctx,
  ticketAction: action,
  ticketData,
  timerData,
  scheduledAt: new Date(now.getTime() + (timerData.minutes || 1435) * 60 * 1000)
    .toISOString().slice(0, 19).replace('T', ' ')
}}];
```

---

### ★ NODE 5: Execute Ticket SQL — MySQL Node

```sql
-- إذا كان action = 'create'
INSERT INTO crm_tickets 
  (crm_lead_id, crm_ticket_type_id, title, created)
VALUES 
  ({{ $json.lead_id }}, {{ $json.ticketData.ticket_type_id }}, 
   '{{ $json.ticketData.title }}', NOW())

-- إذا كان action = 'update'  
UPDATE crm_tickets 
SET updated = NOW(), last_timer_time = NOW()
WHERE id = {{ $json.ticketData.ticket_id }}
```

> **ملاحظة:** استخدم **IF Node** قبله للتفريق بين create وupdate.

---

### ★ NODE 6: Save Message + Timer — MySQL Node (مجمّع)

```sql
-- أولاً: سجّل الرسالة
INSERT INTO crm_ticket_messages 
  (crm_ticket_id, router_value, message_text, sender_type, created)
VALUES 
  ({{ $json.ticketId }}, 
   '{{ $json.output }}',
   '{{ $json.chatInput }}',
   'customer',
   NOW());

-- ثانياً: ألغِ أي Timer قديم pending للتذكرة
UPDATE crm_ticket_timers 
SET status = 'cancelled' 
WHERE crm_ticket_id = {{ $json.ticketId }} 
  AND status = 'pending';

-- ثالثاً: أنشئ Timer جديد
INSERT INTO crm_ticket_timers 
  (crm_ticket_id, timer_type, sequence_no, scheduled_at, status)
VALUES 
  ({{ $json.ticketId }}, 
   '{{ $json.timerData.timer_type }}',
   1,
   '{{ $json.scheduledAt }}',
   'pending');
```

